{"tid":1264871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7.1 戰術召集","createTime":"2019-06-29T01:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:04:27.000Z","uid":241240,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87f5a2c9c0652d636d35b419f3e3a8fa6c0b4adf","tid":1264871,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:54:06.000Z","msg":"追左咁多post之後, 睇黎7.1會有一次總攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n故開此post 想腦風暴一下當日可以有咩戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等小弟黎個拋磚引玉，引諸葛亮s出黎:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聲煞:</span></strong></span><br />\n7.1當日，扯旗禮嘅時候必須配合義勇軍進行曲<br />\n使一眾高官貴人(以下簡稱為汁男) 係大台嘅直播或轉播中成功擠出液體<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聲煞 - 可以話係其中一項有效阻止汁男交戲, 當然更希望能夠達至&quot;不舉&quot;&quot;嘅效果, , 嘅戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRkbg0p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRkbg0p.png&h=fabd790e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(概念圖)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>當然，咩歌曲係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1: sing hallelujah to the lord</span></strong><br />\n眾所周知，能有效淨化心靈，使汁男嘅性欲係聖頌之下得以消除<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2: 東京熱</span></strong><br />\n相信一眾高官都好熟悉<br />\n主要係令液體出錯位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oMdoSB7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoMdoSB7.jpg&h=b06107f5&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3: 多重國歌術</span></strong> <br />\n做法: 國歌奏起之際隨即跟上播放更多國歌，造成聲軌亂疊嘅效果<br />\n效果: 打亂汁男嘅節奏，令高潮位錯亂"},{"pid":"9d6e135411e7fd93b7c2c81bd14f100cdc4ac5d4","tid":1264871,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor